---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Helm"
  description="Your privacy is crucial to us. Learn how Helm collects, uses, protects, and shares information when you visit our website."
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[200px] sm:min-h-[300px] flex items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/privacy-page/privacy-page-banner-bg.jpg');">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-900 bg-opacity-70"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-20">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-yellow-400 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl">

        <!-- 1. Introduction -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Welcome to Helm's Privacy Policy. Your privacy is crucial to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, protect, and share information when you visit https://helm.ceo/ (the "Website").
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Information Collection -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">2. Information Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Personal Information: We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us through contact forms available throughout our Website. This includes your first name, last name, company name, email address, and phone number. Cookies and Usage Data: We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track activity on our Website and store certain information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Use of Information -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">3. Use of Information</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The information we collect helps us provide and improve our services, including staffing and coaching. We use your personal information to contact you, respond to your inquiries, send you requested information about our services and schedule meetings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Information Sharing -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">4. Information Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We may share your information with service providers who assist us in meeting business operations needs, including hosting, data analysis, and communications. We ensure these parties are obligated to protect your information and use it solely for the purposes we dictate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. User Rights -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">5. User Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data stored with us. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at support@helm.ceo
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. Security Measures -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">6. Security Measures</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Helm takes the security of your data seriously. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. In compliance with the New York SHIELD Act, we maintain stringent data security protocols.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 7. Data Breach Notification -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">7. Data Breach Notification</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            In the event of a data breach involving personal information, we will notify affected individuals in accordance with New York State law requirements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 8. Updates to the Privacy Policy -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">8. Updates to the Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Revised" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy frequently to stay informed of our privacy practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 9. How We Use Your Information -->
        <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">9. How We Use Your Information.</h2>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            a. We may use your information to provide and improve our services, respond to inquiries, send you marketing communications, and personalize your experience on our website.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            b. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in operating our website or conducting our business.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            c. No mobile information will be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes. All other categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
